<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>SINGLE REDUCTION, TANDEM DRIVE AXLES: EATON - LUBRICATION - LUBE CHANGE INTERVALS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>LUBE CHANGE INTERVALS</title>
        <para>When filled with an Eaton approved synthetic lubricant at the factory, the initial drain is not required.
            Change the lubricant within the first 5,000 miles of operation when not using a Roadranger approved
            synthetic lubricant in either a new axle or after a carrier head replacement.
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Remove metallic particles from the magnetic filler plug and drain plugs. Clean or replace the
                    breather at each lubricant change.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
